title: NATO Chief Jens Stoltenberg Talks With His Hands [VIDEO] | The Daily Caller
text:
TOP 5491840 
Jens Stoltenberg, NATO’s secretary general, held a joint press conference with Vice President Mike Pence in Brussels on Monday. 
Pence touched on President Trump’s promise to hold NATO countries accountable for military commitments, a point which Stoltenberg emphasized with an expert display of Trumpian hand-talking. (VIDEO: Pence — I Was ‘Dissapointed’ When I Found Out About Flynn) 
WATCH: 
Stoltenberg claims to be Norwegian, but based on the show he put on, he’s definitely got a little Italian in him.
